EventWatchdog     WARNING Other 2s passed
EventWatchdog        INFO Current memory usage is virtual size = # MB, resident set size = # MB
EventWatchdog     WARNING Other 2s passed
EventWatchdog        INFO Current memory usage is virtual size = # MB, resident set size = # MB
EventWatchdog     WARNING Other 2s passed
EventWatchdog        INFO Current memory usage is virtual size = # MB, resident set size = # MB
